                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="76r">Fols 76r and following</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4548Salam">Salām-hymn to Krǝstos Śamrā</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምኪ፡ ለክርስቶስ፡ ሠምረቱ። እንዘ፡ ይብል፡ ካህን፡ እንተ፡ አንበቦ፡
